pi-gen-micro (0.6.0) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Major ergonomics and structural overhaul
  * Add --help, --list-configurations, --list-packages CLI options
  * Add input validation with helpful error messages for missing/invalid
    configurations
  * Add manpage (pi-gen-micro.1)
  * Reorganise project layout: helper-packages/, internal/apt,
    internal/prebuilts, internal/packages, internal/lib
  * Add description files to configurations, description fields to
    helper package nfpm.yaml
  * Add build-packages tool to rebuild helper .deb packages from nfpm
    sources
  * Automatically rebuild helper packages at build time when nfpm is
    available
  * Refactor pi-gen-micro into sourced libraries: dpkg.sh, devices.sh,
    init-systemd.sh, init-busybox.sh
  * Add SYSTEMD=0 component flag for busybox init alternative (inittab,
    rcS, udhcpc networking)
  * Replace device target if-chain with case-based dispatch and shared
    overlay helpers
  * Extract networking setup into install_networking with init-specific
    implementations
  * Fix cryptkey-fetch-otp: return -> exit for standalone execution
  * Fix command injection in generic_delete.list processing
  * Document configuration system, helper packages, and target devices
    in README

